<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBufferOutput.HasCapturedOutput" Title="HasCapturedOutput method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBufferOutput">IFrameBufferOutput</PageRef> ->
    HasCapturedOutput
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>HasCapturedOutput</TypeRef> method returns true if there is image data ready to be read from the output buffer.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool HasCapturedOutput() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        True if output has been captured and can be read, false otherwise.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
